parameters.name: from_date
parameters.description: The date in yyyy-mm-dd format to begin querying from. This date is inclusive.

parameters.name: to_date
parameters.description: The date in yyyy-mm-dd format to query to. This date is inclusive.

parameters.name: limit
parameters.description: The max number of events to be returned.

parameters.name: event
parameters.description: The event or events that you wish to get data for, encoded as a JSON array.

parameters.name: where
parameters.description: An expression to filter events by.

200.description: Success. The return is format is one event per line sorted by increasing timestamp. Each line is a valid JSON object, but the full return itself is JSONL.
